<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Winged" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Winged,</orth> 1) furnished with wings: <bibl n="shak. luc 1728" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1728</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. son 51.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 51, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 2.1.18" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. II, 1, 18</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 1.1.235" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. I, 1, 235</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 4.1.142" default="NO" valid="yes">As IV, 1, 142</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 4.4.2" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A IV, 4, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 2.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II Chor.</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h5 2.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II Chor.</bibl> V Chor. <bibl n="shak. h5 2.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II Chor.</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.3.16" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 3, 16</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.1.267" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 1, 267</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 2.1.88" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 II, 1, 88</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 2.3.123" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 3, 123</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 2.2.28" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 2, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 3.7.66" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. III, 7, 66</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 3.5.61" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 5, 61</bibl>. Per. <bibl n="shak. cym 4.0." default="NO" valid="yes">IV Prol. 47</bibl>.<lb />2) covered by a side body of troops: <cit><quote>whose puissance on either side shall be well w. with our chiefest horse,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 5.3.300" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 V, 3, 300</bibl></cit>.
